        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIGURE 1. Examples of 19th century MAMU specimen tags.A, Masters tag post-1889 (M.386, possible syntype of Halmaturus crassipes Ramsay); B, characteristically compact Masters tag (M.1155, Isoodon obesulus [Shaw]), and C, Ramsay tag (M.468, syntype of I. auratus [Ramsay]). Not to scale." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4806683/files/figure.png" .

